: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudolph_Valentino\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"pockets!).\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheBig Little Liesstar kept things fairly simple with the rest of her outfit, adding some white slingback pumps from Charles & Keith and-of course-a shiny Omega watch in rose gold.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0372541631436244e-11, \"text\": \"Omega\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Sunday, the teen looked ready for business in a refined co-ord that featured a cropped button-up vest and wide-leg pants, both pieces made of a slate gray fabric.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For some extra oomph, she added strappy metallic silver sandals and some gold jewelry-including her own Omega timepiece.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0372541631436244e-11, \"text\": \"Omega\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kidman has made theOlympicsa family affair, arriving in Paris with husband Keith Urban and their other daughter, 13-year-old Faith Margaret.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8184222821727718e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1183, \"end\"